      "description": "Up for sale is a driver-focused 2004 BMW M3 featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six power plant. This high-revving engine utilizes individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing to deliver a linear power band all the way to its 8,000 RPM redline. The drivetrain is anchored by a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory limited-slip M-differential. The chassis is well-sorted, featuring a recently inspected rear subframe and refreshed bushings to maintain the integrity of its multi-link rear suspension. Braking performance remains sharp with ventilated rotors and multi-piston calipers. While the interior shows honest patina consistent with its mileage, the mechanical vitals are robust, making this an ideal specimen for the purist seeking a visceral, analog driving experience.",
